Create a new CryptoKey within a KeyRing. CryptoKey.purpose and CryptoKey.version_template.algorithm are required.
Auto-naming is currently not supported for this resource.
Note - this resource's API doesn't support deletion. When deleted, the resource will persist
on Google Cloud even though it will be deleted from Pulumi state.

<h4 id="cryptokeyversiontemplate">Crypto<wbr>Key<wbr>Version<wbr>Template</h4>

            title="Required">

        <span class="property-type"><a href="#cryptokeyversiontemplatealgorithm">Pulumi.<wbr>Google<wbr>Native.<wbr>Cloudkms.<wbr>V1.<wbr>Crypto<wbr>Key<wbr>Version<wbr>Template<wbr>Algorithm</a></span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}Algorithm to use when creating a CryptoKeyVersion based on this template. For backwards compatibility, GOOGLE_SYMMETRIC_ENCRYPTION is implied if both this field is omitted and CryptoKey.purpose is ENCRYPT_DECRYPT.{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">

    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}ProtectionLevel to use when creating a CryptoKeyVersion based on this template. Immutable. Defaults to SOFTWARE.{{% /md %}}</dd></dl>
